00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:10.977
We see that-- how many people
don't have this capacity

00:05:10.977 --> 00:05:14.247
to actually step back and self
analyze the way you just did,

00:05:14.247 --> 00:05:15.048
you see?

00:05:15.048 --> 00:05:17.082
AUDIENCE: I like
to analyze myself.

00:05:17.082 --> 00:05:19.419
MICHEL DEGRAFF: Yeah,
but that's something

00:05:19.419 --> 00:05:21.154
that you're sharing
with other people that

00:05:21.154 --> 00:05:25.158
might help them a lot, you
know, because it frees you

00:05:25.158 --> 00:05:27.226
to be able to do that, right?

00:05:27.226 --> 00:05:28.261
AUDIENCE: Sometimes.

00:05:28.261 --> 00:05:29.829
MICHEL DEGRAFF: It's a
